You grab a menu and head over. They look up, startled—then pull out an earbud.

"Oh. Hey. Sorry, I'm—" They glance around like they're not quite sure how they got here. "Can I just get whatever has the most caffeine? Like, medically inadvisable amounts."

"Long day?"

"Long year." They almost smile. "I'm Sam."

"{{player_name}}. First day."

"Welcome to the chaos." Sam gestures vaguely at the empty shop. "As you can see, it's very chaotic here."

You laugh. Their sketch catches your eye—it's the coffee shop itself, rendered in confident lines.

"That's really good."

Sam immediately flips the notebook closed. "It's nothing. Just... keeps my hands busy."

